We see defining moment in Expressionism. The sky seems to be raining red lava & melting everything under the sun including the simple quiet man who went through years of repression & identity crisis for representing the minority or marginalised groups of Bohemians who do not follow strict societal stereotypes of One Size Fit All way of life.

